OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with some late spells of
OL,7,Fsunshine. Overnight cloud will
OL,8,Fgradually spread in from the west with
OL,9,Fsome rain arriving by dawn, drier in
OL,10,Fthe east. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FSome early brightness
OL,13,Fpossible, otherwise a grey day on
OL,14,FMonday with a band of rain gradually
OL,15,Fmoving eastwards. The rain heavy at
OL,16,Ftimes, especially during the afternoon
OL,17,Fand evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
